#ad This Barbie LOVES ice cream 😄🍦✨

Visiting Kenya, Africa was truly a life changing experience. It brought me so much joy seeing the animals in their natural habitat and I loved meeting and spending time with the people of Kenya who are beautiful inside & out. 🦁🦓🐆🐘🦛🦏🌿☀️

Being there was also the greatest peace I’ve experienced. 🫶🏽 💆🏾‍♀️

I encourage everyone to go out and see the world. You’ll be inspired in more ways than one once you step out from what you’re used to. 🌍

Thank you Africa. I will be back for sure. ❤️💚🖤

📹KENYA, AFRICA RECAP: As a big fan of The Lion King, this was the real life version of it! Boy was I geekin’ out when I saw Simba, Nala, Mufasa, the hyenas, and Pumbaa up close. And I got to go to Pride Rock!🦁👑 🌳🪨😭🙌🏽🧡

Greatest experience of my life and to the people of Kenya, thank you for being amazing! 🫶🏽❤️🖤💚
Nerd things.🤓💥⚡️✨ #SDCC

Happy birthday Hip-Hop! @imroxanneshante is one of the pioneers in hip-hop. Her flow was dope, she wasn’t afraid to call someone out on a track, she’s the godmother of battle rap, and she paved the way for other female rappers. Thank you Roxanne Shanté for your contributions to Hip-Hop.❤️ 🎤 🎶📀 🥳🎉 #HipHop50 #80s

Heirs of Afrika put together a beautiful luncheon & award ceremony yesterday that brought together Black women from around the world to celebrate sisterhood and honor women who are dynamic representations in various industries. 🫶🏽🎉

Koshie Mills’ mission is to connect Africa with the diaspora and the diaspora to Africa. 

Thank you @koshiemills for being a light in this world and for reminding us to recognize the power of our presence. 🧡💜

💄: @themakeuppaige 
💃💍: handmade by the wonderful people I met in Kenya,Africa
End of summer moments☀️🫶🏽

Our mentor & hip-hop pioneer Lady B is so dope! We loved seeing her in her element at her annual Basement Party concert which she hosted and put together. It was also beautiful to see her get an award for her contributions to hip-hop which was presented by hip-hop legend MC Lyte. 🙌🏽💐 

Lady B constantly celebrates hip-hop artists and she continues to give them amazing opportunities just as she did when she first started out. Back in the day, she was the one that believed in their music and played their records on the radio when no one else did. 

Also, it’s because of her that we were able to meet all of our favorites from the golden age of hip-hop over the years and we are forever grateful for that! 😭❤️🥹

We love you @therealladyb ! ❤️🎶🎙
September highlights. 🎬✨🍂

Girl Power✌🏽❤️🇬🇧😄 I met my favorite Spice Girl today! 😭 Forever grateful for @gerihalliwellhorner and the rest of the Spice Girls’ impact on me and for teaching me the importance of staying true yourself, friendship, spreading positivity, and to have the confidence to stand up for what you believe in.

Anytime I see photos, watch videos of the Spice Girls, or listen  to their music it brings me instant joy! 

I absolutely loved that their mantra, ‘Girl Power’ was consistent in everything they did and with Geri’s new novel, “Rosie Frost and the Falcon Queen,” the theme of Girl Power continues.

Be sure to get your copy of Geri’s novel today! 📚❤️
EAGLES in LA! 🦅🏈💚 5-0 baby! 🙌🏽🎉

Happy birthday @mariolopez !🥳🎉 it’s such a joy working with you everyday! You really are like a big brother to me! Thank you for always giving me great advice and for reminding me to utilize all of my gifts!🎭🕺🏽
😗💃🏽 vintage dresses for the win!

Loved interviewing the hosts of @wildkingdomtv ! As a lover of wildlife, I am so happy this show exists because it highlights conservation success stories around the world. 

I also loved that they brought an Australian blue-tongued skink and an African hedgehog to join in on the fun! 

You can watch their show Saturday mornings on NBC! 🦚

Ginger Spice 😉✌🏽🧡❤️🎃”Say You’ll Be There”.

Outfit made by: @starrland 
Makeup by: @stephanie.a.smith 
Wig by: @hollywoodcustomwigs 

P.S, I always plan out what I’m going to be for Halloween 2-3 years in advance and I had no idea that the year I wrote to be Geri, would be the year I would meet her! Legit just met her last week at her book signing!😭🥹😭🙌🏽 talk about perfecting timing!

It was an honor to produce Geri’s segment! 😭🧡 she was absolutely fantastic and I’m even more inspired by her after spending time with her. 🥹 Thank you @gerihalliwellhorner for your kind words that made me tear up and I look forward to seeing you again when you come back to America!

Also, she loved that I just dressed like her for Halloween! 😭🙌🏽🧡 I’m truly amazed at how everything aligned so perfectly this month😭 WOW!
Weekend in Atlanta to see our mom @janetjackson 🥳🎉🎶💃🏽 We love her so much and she was PHENOMENAL! We cried tears of joy throughout the whole show.🥹😭❤️

Mariah Carey concert!🎄❤️❄️🙌🏽 It was such a wonderful festive show from top to bottom! @mariahcarey is phenomenal! Love her! 😍❤️🐑 🦋 #MariahSZN

Produced my big bro Kel! Loved having him on the show! He brought so much joy to the set! I’m forever grateful for his mentorship & friendship. Big love to you @iamkelmitchell and congrats Good Burger 2! 🍔🧡💚

P.S, if y’all haven’t seen GB2 yet please do, it’s a fantastic sequel and it’s the #1 most streamed Paramount + original movie! 👏🏽🎉
Weekend vibes.😎

The Grammy Salute to 50 Years of Hip-Hop concert was epic!! So many of our hip-hop heroes rocked the stage, we legit geeked out over every performance and it was awesome seeing the duo who made history by winning the first-ever Grammy award for hip-hop, DJ Jazzy Jeff and The Fresh Prince, perform on stage together! 😭🙌🏽❤️So happy that we got to witness this monumental moment in person and yes, we def lost our voices after this concert! 😆🎶🎵🎤

Tune in tonight on CBS and Paramount Plus to see the whole show!
Festive🎄🎁💃🏽
Our Eagles won! Merry Christmas😄🙌🏽🦅💚🎄🎁 Also, our dad got some moves 😆

Had an amazing time at the Australia Zoo & the Crocodile Lodge! 🐊 🦘🐨

The Irwin’s have a special place in our hearts and I absolutely love the incredible ways the family, zoo, and lodge keep Steve Irwin’s legacy alive.

Also, the staff at the zoo and lodge are top tier! Everyone is so lovely!!

Photos from our shoot with the Australia Zoo! 😭💚🙌🏽 You’ll be able to see us in the zoo’s marketing/promos this year! 

This is such a blessing and it means the world to us to be apart of the Irwin’s legacy! Thank you @dwanisoni for making this happen! 

📸 ‘s by the amazing @kateberryphotography 

We also loved visiting the Australia Zoo Wildlife Hospital. They have provided lifesaving treatment to 120,000 sick, injured and orphaned wildlife. 

Steve Irwin said “when people touch an animal, the animal touches their heart and instantly, we’ve won the over to the conservation of that species.” I encourage everyone to see their favorite animal this year in real life and also see how you can help with wildlife conservation.💚
Loved that we kicked off the new year down under! Australia is amazing and so are the people! We will definitely be coming back!! 🇦🇺🦘🐨

From pajama sets to duffel bags, everything in this collection is dope! Thank you @cakeworthy for sending me these pieces! It brought me so much joy! 🥲💖

If you want to be as cool as the @powerrangers , check out the Cakeworthy website to see what other items are available!
